st basic form, schnitzel is a slice of meat, often pounded until fairly thin, then breaded and fried.',3,'00:00:25','00:00:20',4,3123075),(3122013,'Beef Stir-Fry','Cooking',3128005,'Beef Stir-Fry is a quick and flavorful dish made with thinly sliced beef, colorful vegetables, and a savory stir-fry sauce',2,'00:00:15','00:00:10',4,3123002),(3122014,'Apple Turnovers','Pastry',3128001,'Apple turnovers are delicious flaky pastries filled with sweet cinnamon-spiced apples, perfect for breakfast or dessert',2,'00:00:20','00:00:25',6,3123043),(3122015,'Chocolate Chip Cookies','Pastry',3128001,'Chocolate chip cookies are classic, chewy cookies loaded with chocolate chips, perfect for satisfying your sweet tooth',2,'00:00:15','00:00:15',24,3123042),(3122016,'Tomato Basil Bruschetta','Cooking',3128008,'Tomato basil bruschetta is a delicious appetizer made with toasted bread slices topped with a mixture of diced tomatoes, fresh basil, garlic, olive oil, and balsamic vinegar.',1,'00:00:15','00:00:05',6,3123009),(3122017,'Mushroom Risotto','Cooking',3128002,'Mushroom risotto is a creamy Italian rice dish cooked with mushrooms, onions, garlic, white wine, and Parmesan cheese, resulting in a rich and flavorful meal',3,'00:00:10','00:00:30',4,3123010),(3122018,'Beef Tacos','Cooking',3128009,'Beef tacos are a popular Mexican dish consisting of seasoned ground beef served in tortillas and topped with various ingredients such as lettuce, cheese, tomatoes, and salsa',1,'00:00:10','00:00:15',6,3123012),(3122019,' Lemon Garlic Shrimp Pasta','Cooking',3128005,'Lemon garlic shrimp pasta is a flavorful dish featuring succulent shrimp cooked in a buttery garlic and lemon sauce, tossed with cooked pasta and fresh parsley',2,'00:00:15','00:00:15',4,3123045),(3122020,'Blueberry Muffins','Pastry',3128001,'Bursting with juicy blueberries and a tender crumb, perfect for a quick treat anytime.',1,'00:00:10','00:00:25',6,3123073),(3122021,'Profiterol Banoffe','Pastry',3128003,'An irresistible combin