xture, making them a beloved treat enjoyed during festive occasions across cultures.',4,'00:00:30','00:00:20',9,3123025),(3122048,'BÃ¶rek','Pastry',3128010,'A savory Turkish pastry with thin dough layers filled with cheese, spinach, or minced meat, baked until crispy and golden, enjoyed as a versatile snack or meal.',3,'00:00:40','00:00:30',8,3123022),(3122049,'Spanish Tortilla','Cooking',3128011,'A tortilla filled with eggs and creamy vegetables',2,'00:00:10','00:00:20',2,3123011),(3122050,'Cauliflower steaks ','Cooking',3128005,'If you are looking for the perfect way to cook your cauliflower, this is the recipe you have to try! Prepare well-seasoned cauliflower steaks and bake them in the oven until golden and crispy!',2,'00:00:25','00:00:20',8,3123142),(3122051,'Cheese and bacon stuffed mushrooms','Cooking',3128010,'Cheese and bacon stuffed mushrooms are savory appetizers bursting with flavor and texture. Large mushroom caps are filled with a rich mixture of cream cheese, shredded cheese, crispy bacon bits, and aromatic seasonings like garlic and herbs.',2,'00:00:15','00:00:25',6,3123057),(3122052,'Pickled onion','Cooking',3128010,'Upgrade your dishes by adding a little homemade pickled onion! Follow the recipe and prepare this flavorful delicacy easily and quickly!',1,'00:00:10','00:00:05',3,3123003),(3122053,'Oven-baked sweet potato fries','Cooking',3128011,'Oven-baked sweet potato fries are a healthier alternative to traditional fries, offering a satisfying crunch with a naturally sweet flavor.',2,'00:00:10','00:00:30',4,3123144),(3122054,'Baked sweet potatoes with eggs','Cooking',3128011,'The result is a delicious combination of creamy sweet potato and perfectly cooked eggs, making for a satisfying and flavorful dish that\'s as easy to make as it is delicious to eat.',3,'00:00:15','00:00:00',4,3123144);
